<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1810,1832]" pageId="12" pageNumber="109">FIGURE 2.</emphasis>
50% majority rule consensus cladogram of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Rotheray and Gilbert" baseAuthorityYear="1999" box="[722,812,1810,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Bacchini">
<emphasis box="[722,812,1810,1832]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="109">Bacchini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species produced from Bayesian analysis of COI data. Clade supports shown are posterior probabilities.
</paragraph>
</caption>
